content:
ISLAMABAD, Mar 22 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Tuesday that today was a historic day under the leadership of Prime Minister Imran Khan as  second meeting of the Organization of Islamic Cooperation was being held in Pakistan within the last three months.
Using his twitter handle, Farrukh Habib said in December 2021 a special OIC session was convened on the situation in Afghanistan and now 48th session of OIC Foreign Ministers Council meeting was being hosted by Pakistan.
